            <p>The Seed Fund is in a period of transition where we are migrating from our old web property to this one. To learn more about the Seed Fund you can checkout our <a href="http://www.sbs.ox.ac.uk/ideas-impact/entrepreneurship/venture-creation/seed-fund/expression-interest-form">old webpage</a>, with special attention to the <a href="http://www.sbs.ox.ac.uk/ideas-impact/entrepreneurship/venture-creation/seed-fund/faqs">Frequently Asked Questions</a> section.</p>
            <p>We always enjoy hearing from entrepreneurs, whether you are looking for funding or want to develop your idea. Send an email to <a href="mailto:hello@sbsseedfund.com">hello@sbsseedfund.com</a> or come visit us at the Oxford LaunchPad in Saïd Business School.</p>
            <p>If you are an investor, mentor, or incoming student interested in participating in the Seed Fund during the 2014-2015 academic year, please email <a href="mailto:hello@sbsseedfund.com">hello@sbsseedfund.com</a>.</p>
            <p>For other enquiries, write to <a href="mailto:entrepreneurship@sbs.ox.ac.uk">entrepreneurship@sbs.ox.ac.uk</a> or call +44 (0)1865 288845.</p>
